{"tid":1610820,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【香港警察，必須解散】黑警開真槍後新口號","createTime":"2019-10-01T21:05:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T11:06:31.000Z","uid":168384,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"588acdae28c8ae939fade3e53ed3ab9097e39129","tid":1610820,"uid":168384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T21:05:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">當開咗真槍殺人之後，我想全香港人都唔好唔記得，成個運動其實係揭發咗另一個主要危機：黑警<br />\n<br />\n除非黑警吞槍自殺，如果唔係<span style=\"color: red;\">佢哋仲會永遠為港共政府服務</span> 黑警一日仲喺度返工，香港仲係會有班毅進仔搞事<br />\n以後每日出街每區左近都有<span style=\"color: red;\">一班隨便殺人既有牌黑社會</span> 咁仲點保障到自由，講句野就開槍，同生活喺大陸有咩分別</span><br />\n<br />\n唔該傳句口號出去，唔好忘記10.1國殤日<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>香港警察，必須解散</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"6de75fff8fac63a92a9c63112a11af1cec06897a","tid":1610820,"uid":168384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T21:14:52.000Z","msg":"個鑊肯肯定魔警孭㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"660a685d179317c1f5956e8f11e1f21a86c6ef9c","tid":1610820,"uid":5701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T21:20:23.000Z","msg":"解散同清算係必須既<br />\n不過係咪要諗埋解散完之後 應該揾邊個黎暫代/取代班狗？<br />\n唔想又係淨係嗌個口號 得個講字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96173869e0548645e3eed04462ac120dfb9c6860","tid":1610820,"uid":168384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T21:33:28.000Z","msg":"都啱，真正既革命宜家先開始，一切慢慢嚟，唔好太急"},{"pid":"c56b9a9f48894b6449a028b3e1afb5f4806f1a71","tid":1610820,"uid":178364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T21:43:57.000Z","msg":"香港警察，必須解散"},{"pid":"63108e4488e4fc1e9987525d50eabec2342adde1","tid":1610820,"uid":67156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:06:31.000Z","msg":"重組"}